=== Noun ===
'''flame''' ([[flames]])

# The visible part of [[fire]].
# Girlfriend, lover in usually short-lived but passionate affair.
# Insulting criticism or remark meant to incite anger. [[Internet]]
# (''colour'') a brilliant reddish orange colour, like that of a flame.
